response.overview: In the first day of the new year GCW presents 56 Nights live on FITE! The event features The Do or Die Rumble and gets into the new year with a bang. You can check below and the first two matches from the lineup:  Do Or Die Scramble (Winner enters Rumble at #30)  Joey Janela vs Blake Christian vs Tony Deppen vs Willie Mack vs Alec Price vs Jordan Oliver  Maki Iton vs Sawyer Wreck vs Billie Starkz vs Dark Sheik  Matt Tremont vs Mad Man Pondo  Masha Slamovich vs Cole Radrick  Nick Wayne vs Liam Slater  The Do or Die Rumble  *lineup subject to change
response.title: GCW 56 Nights
